<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire is likely infrequent in stands due to lack of fine fuels and wide spacing of shrubs. <i>Psorothamnus </i>spp. are likely top-killed and sprout weakly from the base after fires. However, hot fires may eliminate all plants, requiring off-site seed sources to reestablish stands.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
